<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NTM8.7">
<l>caṅkamā kaṭalkaṭaintāṉ taṇmukilkāḷ vēṅkaṭattuc</l>
<l>ceṅkaṇmāl cēvaṭikkīḻa ṭivīḻcci viṇṇappam</l>
<l>koṅkaimēṟ kuṅkumattiṉ kuḻampaḻiyap pukuntorunāḷ</l>
<l>taṅkumē leṉṉāvi taṅkumeṉ ṟuraiyīrē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O cool clouds from Vēṅkaṭam of Him who churned the great ocean</l>
<l rend="indent">[that possesses] conches!</l>
<l>Here is [my] request with prostration at red-eyed Māl’s red feet:</l>
<l>Tell [Him] that if He stays for one day, entering [me] so that the saffron paste</l>
<l rend="indent">on [my] breasts gets effaced,</l>
<l>my life[breath] will be sustained!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
